HEADWORD: Undeserver
<hw>Un`de*serv"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of no merit;
one who is nor deserving or worthy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
